dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Valleton quadrangle, Monterey County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Valleton CA 1948. Photorevised 1973. AMS 1855 I NW - series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent field work 2003.
